<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Credencial SIUT-ITSM</title>
  <style>
    @page {
      margin: 0;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: DejaVu Sans, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #0f172a;
    }

    .card-page {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #ffffff;
    }

    .stripe-red {
      position: absolute;
      top: -26px;
      right: -68px;
      width: 235px;
      height: 92px;
      background: #c8102e;
      border-radius: 0 0 0 140px;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .stripe-blue {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -38px;
      left: -74px;
      width: 245px;
      height: 100px;
      background: #0a3d91;
      border-radius: 0 150px 0 0;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      padding: 12px;
      height: calc(100% - 24px);
    }

    .logo-row {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .logo-row td {
      text-align: center;
      vertical-align: middle;
      width: 33.33%;
      height: 30px;
    }

    .logo-row img {
      max-height: 26px;
      max-width: 66px;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .holder-name {
      margin: 2px 0 2px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0a3d91;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      line-height: 1.15;
    }

    .holder-role {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 8px;
      color: #334155;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    }

    .avatar {
      width: 84px;
      height: 84px;
      margin: 0 auto 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 4px solid #0a3d91;
      background: #f1f5f9;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 84px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #64748b;
    }

    .avatar img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .org {
      margin: 0 auto 8px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 7px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      color: #1e293b;
      width: 94%;
    }

    .imss {
      margin: 0 auto 8px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 8px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0f172a;
    }

    .vigencia-front {
      margin: 0 auto 8px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 8px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0a3d91;
    }

    .qr {
      width: 82px;
      height: 82px;
      margin: 0 auto 4px;
      border: 2px solid #0f172a;
      background: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      vertical-align: middle;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .qr img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .qr-help {
      margin: 0;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 6.5px;
      color: #334155;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .site {
      margin: 3px 0 0;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 7px;
      color: #0a3d91;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .back-title {
      margin: 2px 0 8px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0a3d91;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    }

    .back-text {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1.35;
      color: #1e293b;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    .vigencia-box {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      padding: 6px;
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      background: #f8fafc;
    }

    .vigencia-label {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 7px;
      color: #475569;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    }

    .vigencia-value {
      margin: 2px 0 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0a3d91;
    }

    .sign-area {
      border-top: 1px solid #94a3b8;
      padding-top: 8px;
      margin-top: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .sign-name {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 8.5px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0f172a;
    }

    .sign-role {
      margin: 2px 0 3px;
      font-size: 7px;
      color: #334155;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    }

    .sign-hash {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 6px;
      color: #1f2937;
      word-break: break-all;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .meta {
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 6.7px;
      color: #334155;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .meta p {
      margin: 0 0 3px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
<section class="card-page">
  <div class="stripe-red"></div>
  <div class="stripe-blue"></div>

  <div class="content">
    <table class="logo-row">
      <tr>
        <td>
          {if !empty($logos['tecnm'])}
            <img src="{$logos['tecnm']|noescape}" alt="Logo TecNM">
          {/if}
        </td>
        <td>
          {if !empty($logos['itsm'])}
            <img src="{$logos['itsm']|noescape}" alt="Logo ITSM">
          {/if}
        </td>
        <td>
          {if !empty($logos['siut'])}
            <img src="{$logos['siut']|noescape}" alt="Logo SIUT">
          {/if}
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p class="holder-name">{$holder['fullName']}</p>
    <p class="holder-role">{$holder['cargo']}</p>

    <div class="avatar">
      {if !empty($holder['photoSrc'])}
        <img src="{$holder['photoSrc']|noescape}" alt="Foto de perfil">
      {else}
        SIN FOTO
      {/if}
    </div>

    <p class="org">{$organization}</p>
    <p class="imss">IMSS: {$holder['imss']}</p>
    <p class="vigencia-front">{$holder['membershipLabel']}</p>

    <div class="qr">
      {if !empty($qrSrc)}
        <img src="{$qrSrc|noescape}" alt="Codigo QR de verificacion">
      {/if}
    </div>

    <p class="qr-help">Escanea para validar vigencia en linea.</p>
    <p class="site">{$website}</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div style="page-break-before: always;"></div>

<section class="card-page">
  <div class="stripe-red"></div>
  <div class="stripe-blue"></div>

  <div class="content">
    <p class="back-title">Acreditacion</p>

    <p class="back-text">
      Se acredita que la persona titular de esta credencial pertenece al padron de afiliados del
      Sindicato Unico de Trabajadores del Instituto Tecnologico Superior de Macuspana,
      en Macuspana, Tabasco.
    </p>

    <div class="vigencia-box">
      <p class="vigencia-label">Vigencia</p>
      <p class="vigencia-value">{$holder['vigencia']}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="sign-area">
      <p class="sign-name">{$signatory['name']}</p>
      <p class="sign-role">{$signatory['role']}</p>
      <p class="sign-hash">Firma digital (hash CURP): {$signatory['signatureHash']}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="meta">
      <p><strong>Emision:</strong> {$issuedAt}</p>
      <p><strong>Verificacion:</strong> {$verificationUrl}</p>
      <p><strong>Domicilio:</strong> {$address}</p>
      <p><strong>RFC:</strong> {$rfc}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</body>

</html>
